track_notes: Set off and keep left of the newly planted copse. Meet track at NT 5920 1534 and then head to the right slightly. Track and path now clear on the ground to the top. Fantastic summit with prominence on all sides. Qualified on 2m FM with 5 QSOs mid-week but needed 40 watts to make it. Vertical dipole used.
track_title: From tree lined avenue opposite drive end for Billerwill

track_notes: There are lots of deer fences in the area. The local said there is a path through the forest. This was quite easy.
